# Autonocraft Crafting & Items

- Sigils: `Crafting/SigilRegistry.cs`
- Station recipes: `Crafting/CraftRecipeRegistry.cs`
- Tools: `Items/ToolRegistry.cs`, mining speed: `Items/MiningCalculator.cs`
- UI: `UI/CrucibleScreen.cs`, `UI/JournalScreen.cs`

Tests to run after changes: `TestSigilBenchActivation`, `TestCruciblePlankRecipe`, `TestNewCraftRecipes`, `TestToolMiningSpeed`, `TestSkillProgression`.

HTTP test: `python3 tests/interact.py action dev cmd_line="unlock recipe:plank"`
